# Deployment Guide

## Prerequisites
- Wallet with Base mainnet ETH
- PRIVATE_KEY in .env
- BASE_MAINNET_RPC in .env

## Deploy to Base Mainnet

```bash
npx hardhat run scripts/deployToken.js --network base
npx hardhat run scripts/deployNFT.js --network base
npx hardhat run scripts/deployStaking.js --network base
npx hardhat run scripts/deployDAO.js --network base
```

## Verify on Basescan
```bash
npx hardhat verify --network base CONTRACT_ADDRESS
```

## Update frontend
Update CONTRACTS in src/constants.ts with mainnet addresses.